NAME
	risk-gauge (display) - render a fixed label/value metric column from a five-field file at the mount path plus two files at sibling paths of the mount

INTERFACE
	display (MatrixDisplay)

READS
	.	the mount path itself is a FILE (e.g. /n/tbl4/risk):
		single line, whitespace fields:
		total_value cash unrealized_pnl portfolio_var position_count
	../portfolio/defense/status	status word - NOTE: resolved
		against the mount's PARENT directory
	../portfolio/risk/var_95	value string - same parent-relative
		resolution

WRITES
	none (renders only)

DESCRIPTION
	Labelled metric rows; the defense status word colour-codes
	(crisis/caution/normal), unrealized P&L colours by sign, and
	unreadable metrics render "--".  Because two reads resolve
	against the parent of the mount, this module's effective
	contract is the mount's parent directory; a namespace that binds
	only the mount file will leave those rows at "--".  The value
	format is plain whitespace text, not JSON.
